com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity

Class MessageStatisticsData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.MessageStatisticsData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MessageStatisticsData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holds the statistics for messages for a given safe ordered object. The statistics include:
    • # of failed messages
    • # of failed messages that can be retried
    • # of inflight messages
    • # of unsent messages
